*Hrabar* čovek prošao je tešku situaciju sa uspehom. (The brave man passed the difficult situation with success.)

Ona voli da bude *hrabra*. (She likes to be brave.)

Njegovoj deci dala je *hrabrost* da veruju u sebe. (She gave her children the courage to believe in themselves.)

On je *hrabar* da istraži nepoznato. (He is brave enough to explore the unknown.)

Oni su se *hrabro* borili za svoje pravo. (They bravely fought for their right.)